EXTRACT ppspwpd1

RMTHOST ggpsppf501.sbg-psp-ppd.a.intuit.com, mgrport 15000, ENCRYPT AES128, TIMEOUT 120, PARAMS -UL

RMTTRAIL ./dirdat/pspepd1/tr
PASSTHRU

discardfile ./dirrpt/ppspwpd1.dsc, megabytes 100, append
discardrollover at 00:01

STATOPTIONS RESETREPORTSTATS
Report at 23:55
ReportRollover at 00:01 on sunday

--REPORTCOUNT EVERY 5 MINTUES RATE

TABLE PSPADM.*;
SEQUENCE PSPADM.*;

